text: Ðis is seo boc æt stoce.
Ærest of þam more on mærce cumb & swa to mærc hamme & swa to hean hammæ.
And swa to þam west hliþe norð &lang to hogebura mearce.
And swa utt to crawan ersce & swa to hean lea & swa be norðan dyrnan hammæ nyþær innan þa ea.
Þys sinð ða ðen into Stoce siblingc hyrst & trowing sceaddas & rocisfald.
